uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.function.annotation

Annotation Type Inputs


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Inputs
    The Inputs annotation is used by Function implementations to report accepted argument types for it's execution method. It is used to enable runtime type checking to ensure that a function is applicable to it's arguments.
